{"tid":515856,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個Leap Year test program...","createTime":"2017-12-31T18:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T01:30:11.000Z","uid":33883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b64a0e52ea920a46a02e17697493770aadf106c","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T18:36:43.000Z","msg":"我試範下先(用bash script):<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">yy=0<br />\nisLeapYear=&quot;false&quot;<br />\n<br />\necho -n &quot;Enter year (yyyy) : &quot;<br />\nread yy<br />\n<br />\n# find out if it is a leap year or not<br />\n<br />\nif [ $((yy % 4)) -ne 0 ] ; then         # If not divisible by 4 (like 2012), then <br />\n:                                       #    jump to fi (i.e. not a leap year), else (i.e. divisible by 4) proceed <br />\nelif [ $((yy % 400)) -eq 0 ] ; then     # if also divisible by 400 (like 2000), then <br />\nisLeapYear=&quot;true&quot;                       #    it's a leap year, else (i.e. divisible by 4 but not 400) proceed<br />\nelif [ $((yy % 100)) -eq 0 ] ; then     # if also divisible by 100 (like 1900), then <br />\n:                                       #    jump to fi (i.e. not a leap year), else (i.e. divisible by 4 but not 400 or 100) then<br />\nelse                                    # it's a leap year.<br />\nisLeapYear=&quot;true&quot;<br />\nfi<br />\n<br />\nif [ &quot;$isLeapYear&quot; == &quot;true&quot; ];<br />\nthen<br />\necho &quot;$yy is a leap year&quot;<br />\nelse<br />\necho &quot;$yy is NOT a leap year&quot;<br />\nfi</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/5XZhuW2g6TSmLFzG97xQu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2F5XZhuW2g6TSmLFzG97xQu8&d=JHEyIOHWQW0oKCPp0nkTI2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=eda89dc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/5XZhuW2g6TSmLFzG97xQu8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mPVd2G/leapyear.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FmPVd2G%2Fleapyear.jpg&h=87ed4f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865d473241c0b2c4f45653813f554dc583857056","tid":515856,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T19:09:22.000Z","msg":"perl <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#!/usr/bin/perl<br />\n<br />\nprint 'Enter year (yyyy): ';<br />\n$y = &lt;STDIN&gt; * 1;<br />\nprint (((($y % 400 &amp;&amp; !($y % 100)) || $y % 4) ? 'no' : 'yes').&quot;\\n&quot;);"},{"pid":"fe0c1473762f423104ac0afb1a7a4df7ce2f6a6e","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T20:22:31.000Z","msg":"Haskell <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <strong>LeapYear.hs</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">module LeapYear where<br />\n<br />\nimport <a href=\"http://System.IO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FSystem.IO&d=JHEyIOHWQW0oKCPp0nkTI2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=e32d51e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">System.IO</a><br />\n<br />\nprompt :: String -&gt; IO String<br />\nprompt text = do<br />\n  putStr text<br />\n  hFlush stdout<br />\n  getLine<br />\n<br />\nisLeapYear :: Int -&gt; Bool<br />\nisLeapYear y<br />\n  | y <code>mod</code> 4 /= 0 = False<br />\n  | y <code>mod</code> 100 /= 0 = True<br />\n  | y <code>mod</code> 400 /= 0 = False<br />\n  | otherwise = True<br />\n<br />\ntoStatement :: Bool -&gt; String<br />\ntoStatement s = if s == True then &quot;is a leap year&quot; else &quot;is NOT a leap year&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmain = do<br />\n  year &lt;- prompt &quot;Enter a year (YYYY): &quot;<br />\n  print ( year ++ &quot; &quot; ++ toStatement (isLeapYear (read year :: Int)) )</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://paste.ofcode.org/CQvbQddsevi8X9J6dxdREe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaste.ofcode.org%2FCQvbQddsevi8X9J6dxdREe&d=JHEyIOHWQW0oKCPp0nkTI2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=b6721998\" target=\"_blank\">https://paste.ofcode.org/CQvbQddsevi8X9J6dxdREe</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/gtXSUw/Leapyear.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FgtXSUw%2FLeapyear.jpg&h=441d5bb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f123b46c0b319de12966a632bd41b203e2a48aa3","tid":515856,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"bash <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 用date command出術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#!/bin/bash<br />\n<br />\necho -n &quot;Enter year (yyyy): &quot;<br />\nread y<br />\n<br />\ndate -d &quot;$y-02-29&quot; &amp;&gt; /dev/null<br />\n<br />\nif [ $? -eq 0 ]; then<br />\n    echo &quot;$y is a leap year.&quot;<br />\nelse<br />\n    echo &quot;$y is NOT a leap year.&quot;<br />\nfi"},{"pid":"41983239c6622c951864c509e4901452aa14aa27","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f123b46c0b319de12966a632bd41b203e2a48aa3","tid":515856,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"bash <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 用date command出術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#!/bin/bash<br />\n<br />\necho -n &quot;Enter year (yyyy): &quot;<br />\nread y<br />\n<br />\ndate -d &quot;$y-02-29&quot; &amp;&gt; /dev/null<br />\n<br />\nif [ $? -eq 0 ]; then<br />\n    echo &quot;$y is a leap year.&quot;<br />\nelse<br />\n    echo &quot;$y is NOT a leap year.&quot;<br />\nfi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b149c16f43cca9c17f7ed4eccf4cb87b7918a1f1","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:04