pyear.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FgtXSUw%2FLeapyear.jpg&h=441d5bb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:14:10.000Z","msg":"isLeapYear :: Int -&gt; Bool<br />\nisLeapYear y = y <code>mod</code> 4 == 0 &amp;&amp; y <code>mod</code> 100 /= 0 &amp;&amp; y <code>mod</code> 400 == 0<br />\n<br />\n會唔會好d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"No, should be like this instead:<br />\nisLeapYear :: Int -&gt; Bool<br />\nisLeapYear y = <span style=\"color: green;\">(</span>y <code>mod</code> 4 == 0 &amp;&amp; y <code>mod</code> 100 /= 0<span style=\"color: green;\">)</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">||</span> y <code>mod</code> 400 == 0<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e92d1e66fc1abac8d3260d7e1a46a2bcb86641","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945ac151ee7df487ff55e17349fef8231f7159e8","tid":515856,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b149c16f43cca9c17f7ed4eccf4cb87b7918a1f1","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"補番個正正常常嘅leap year flowchart先, 上面Haskell個isLeapYear function就係跟足呢個flowchart嚟整架喇:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mEzazw/Leap_Year_Flow_Chart.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FmEzazw%2FLeap_Year_Flow_Chart.jpg&h=46f763d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"x % 400 == 0 || (x % 4 == 0 &amp;&amp; x % 100 != 0)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ea227cfb0862914e68a439e5818b818cef0f25","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c97ab453c2a095d4c6e9170021cbda27a599aa","tid":515856,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c04597f97a7e39f86a4c829c3180ec8e00cae4","tid":515856,"uid":33883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f123b46c0b319de12966a632bd41b203e2a48aa3","tid":515856,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"bash <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 用date command出術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#!/bin/bash<br />\n<br />\necho -n &quot;Enter year (yyyy): &quot;<br />\nread y<br />\n<br />\ndate -d &quot;$y-02-29&quot; &amp;&gt; /dev/null<br />\n<br />\nif [ $? -eq 0 ]; then<br />\n    echo &quot;$y is a leap year.&quot;<br />\nelse<br />\n    echo &quot;$y is NOT a leap year.&quot;<br />\nfi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"BTW, 你呢個bash script如果係32-bit Linux(and also ARM-based Linux)度run, 會有部份dates係invalid, e.g. 1896-02-29, 咁就會搞到1896明明係閏年都變咗唔係! 但如果係64-bit Linux度run就完全冇問題! <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"32bit好似由1902年開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"我試到係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">$ date -d &quot;1901-12-15&quot;<br />\n1901年12月15日 上午 12:00:00<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">$ date -d &quot;1901-12-14&quot;<br />\ndate: invalid date &lsquo;1901-12-14&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n$ date -d &quot;1901-12-13&quot;<br />\ndate: invalid date &lsquo;1901-12-13&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n$ date -d &quot;1896-01-01&quot;<br />\ndate: invalid date &lsquo;1896-01-01&rsquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\ni.e. <ins>1901-12-14或以前唔work</ins>, 之後嘅日期就冇問題!"},{"pid":"a78356efd66b6649930d37d5d441a1c2def73df8","tid":515856,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T14:02:55.0